<h2>Reporting errors</h2>

<p style="font-size: larger;">
    Vanuatu Voices is an open-access tool for the linguistic community and speakers alike. 
    If you would like to suggest an alternative transcription or have found any error in the data presented, please report it at: 
    <a href="https://github.com/lexibank/vanuatuvoices/issues/new/choose">https://github.com/lexibank/vanuatuvoices/issues/new/choose</a>.
    The dataset will be regularly updated and contributors will be added as authors to the dataset.
</p>

<h2>Contributing data</h2>

<p style="font-size: larger;">
    If you would like to propose a dataset for a doculect not already included 
    in Vanuatu Voices, please email us at 
    <a href="mailto:vanuatuvoices@eva.mpg.de">vanuatuvoices@eva.mpg.de</a> with the following information.
Please do not send any recordings,  transcriptions, or data until requested.</p>
